description: Luxury Living at 832 East 3rd St., South Boston. Discover elevated living in this expertly crafted 4-bedroom, 4.5-bath home, designed by a master finish carpenter with custom millwork and refined detail throughout. The spacious layout includes a family room, home gym, and office, offering flexibility for modern lifestyles. The gourmet kitchen is outfitted with Thermador appliances, a wine fridge, and custom cabinetry that seamlessly blends elegance and function. Relax by the stately fireplace or unwind in your private backyard retreat with a deck and patio—ideal for entertaining or peaceful escapes. With gleaming hardwood floors, high-end finishes, a garage plus additional parking, and a prime location near Castle Island, Pleasure Bay, and the Seaport, this home offers beauty, convenience, and timeless appeal. Schedule your private showing today—your South Boston sanctuary awaits!
